bilingual.source: Make sure you have sufficient food, water, medicine and batteries for electrical appliances.
bilingual.target: 确保你有足够的食物、水、药品和电器用的电池。
这份报告缺乏足够的数据。

bilingual.source: We have sufficient time to complete the project.
bilingual.target: 我们有足够的时间完成这个项目。

bilingual.source: We lack sufficient funds to complete the project.
bilingual.target: 我们缺乏足够的资金来完成项目。

bilingual.source: The project lacked sufficient funding to continue.
bilingual.target: 这个项目缺乏足够的资金来继续。

bilingual.source: There is sufficient food for everyone at the party.
bilingual.target: 聚会上有足够的食物供每个人享用。

bilingual.source: She didn't have sufficient courage to confront him.
bilingual.target: 她没有足够的勇气去面对他。

bilingual.source: Without sufficient evidence, it is just a conjecture.
bilingual.target: 没有足够的证据，这只是一个猜测。

bilingual.source: It is not wise to speculate without sufficient evidence.
bilingual.target: 没有足够的证据就推测是不明智的。

bilingual.source: Without sufficient ballast, the boat could easily capsize.
bilingual.target: 没有足够的压舱物，船很容易倾覆。

yingyinNormal.en: There is sufficient evidence to have you both expelled. Yes, sir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这足以让学校把你们开除。是，校长。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: I don't care. Not if Downton is self-sufficient by the end of it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不管，只要最后唐顿可以自食其力就行。

yingyinNormal.en: With sufficient repetition, the animal will associate the sound of the whistle with the discomfort of sea sickness.
yingyinNormal.zh: 重复次数达到一定程度，动物听到尖锐的哨声，就会条件反射产生晕船感。

yingyinNormal.en: The correct answer is when covered by a film of liquid sufficient to reduce the coefficient of static friction between the tire and the road to essentially zero, but not so deep as to introduce a new source of friction.
yingyinNormal.zh: 正确的答案是"当[路面]被覆盖上一层液体足以把轮胎和道路之间的静态摩擦系数减少到理论上的零值又不产生新的摩擦源"。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. & det. 足够的；充足的

word_family.mean: v. 足够；合适；满足…的需求

sense_info_list.en: of a quantity that can fulfil a need but without being abundant

examination_example.sentence: The author concludes that individual efforts are far from <highlight>sufficient</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作者的结论是，个人的努力远远不够。

examination_example.sentence: What makes the problem thornier is that the usual time-management techniques don't seem <highlight>sufficient</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 让问题更加棘手的是，通常的时间管理技术似乎还不够。

examination_example.sentence: A few generative rules are then <highlight>sufficient</highlight> to unfold the entire fundamental structure of a language, which is why children can learn it so quickly.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一些语言生成规则就足以揭开某种语言的全部基础结构，这就是儿童学习语言如此之快的原因。

word_usage.usage:
sufficient和enough都表示“足够的”，区别在于：
日常生活中衡量“量的多少”时，常用enough。
强调“质”的时候，会用sufficient。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
